  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/wearables/\" rel=\"tag\">佩戴产品</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://chinese.engadget.com/2014/02/25/blackberry-currently-has-no-plans-for-a-wearable-device/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/adam/acafcaae5bbb7a0ec91e236ab3051d47/IMG_9778.jpg\" style=\"width: 620px; height: 413px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n如今可穿戴设备十分火热，但 BlackBerry 似乎没有追逐这种潮流的意思，或者说，至少暂时来看，它们没有这方面的打算。在今天的 MWC 发布会上，当被问及相关问题时，CEO 程宗守明确表示了当下无意进入可穿戴设备市场的态度。不过这并不意味着 BlackBerry 将永远与此类产品无缘，只是他们目前心不在此，毕竟眼下有更紧要的任务啊（先盈利再说吧）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n引用来源：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/02/25/blackberry-currently-has-no-plans-for-a-wearable-device/\">Engadget</a></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/25/blackberry-currently-has-no-plans-for-a-wearable-device/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20837484/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/25/blackberry-currently-has-no-plans-for-a-wearable-device/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
